How to

Screenshots:

In testing it is very improtant to take screenshots for verification
so that we can prove that our test case is covered certain functionality.

In order to take a screenshot in Selenium we will be using TakesScreenshot interface.

Calendar:

How to handle calendar:

1. We need to click on Calendar
2. We need to locate the month and get text
3. if the desired text is not visible -- > we click on Next
4. as soon as the desired text is found -- > we need to grab all cells from the body
5. loop through the cells
6. once the cell value is matched with our condition -- > click on the matched value and break the loop.

Why do we need screenshots for our testing?

In testing it is very important to take screenshots in order to prove that our test case covered certain functionality.
In selenium in order to take a screenshot we will be using TakesScreehshot interface.

Actions class:

Actions class is given by selenium to handle keyboard and mouse events such as:
Move to an element
Dragging and dropping
double click
right click

